{"tid":2100184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"趁呢個時候係需要藍絲戰線","createTime":"2020-07-09T00:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T01:47:12.000Z","uid":147226,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"798b7262f36d33e8e0d3cc04574038dd749e7f84","tid":2100184,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:59:25.000Z","msg":"之前一年藍絲一直都唔割席<br />\n相反我地呢邊日日鬥黃<br />\n<br />\n今次國安法生效，係的的確確有班淺藍會驚<br />\n田二少呢啲都開晒名<br />\n呢個時候，鬥藍鬥紅又好，用道理好，咩都好<br />\n總之呢個係最好時機去令藍絲分裂，甚至變黃<br />\n<br />\n要記住，過去一年，阻到我地嘅<br />\n唔係同路人<br />\n係對家<br />\n<br />\n你花每一篇鬥黃嘅文章時間<br />\n換成藍絲戰線<br />\n成個抗爭會好大分別"},{"pid":"4afafd6ab137985adf2db83db1512daa180b72ae","tid":2100184,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:03:03.000Z","msg":"做咩唔遊行反英反美"},{"pid":"b9f4ea43a060325413cd1720557fcfe9a437ee56","tid":2100184,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:11:39.000Z","msg":"藍絲係廢 <br />\n返工搵錢理得香港死"},{"pid":"0036610d48a8360d1d72d60dbc0a9fd0d8523a88","tid":2100184,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9f4ea43a060325413cd1720557fcfe9a437ee56","tid":2100184,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:11:39.000Z","msg":"藍絲係廢 <br />\n返工搵錢理得香港死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:37:37.000Z","msg":"大部分港豬心態係多一事不如少一事<br />\n<br />\n所以對一堆淺藍來講，2020抗爭淡化咗好多，反而國安法搞到外國出晒聲，係多一事<br />\n兩三個月佢地就慣<br />\n所以要叫醒係趁而家<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家額外做好多野<br />\n只係用鬥黃精力轉移過去藍絲"},{"pid":"d0cbb1c3d64a8469fa81bd89e9f9f0604cbce993","tid":2100184,"uid":230942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:44:34.000Z","msg":"唔夠藍果啲跟本係Yc"},{"pid":"b8206ce267452478fa4bd63a30007e09fc0a5fb4","tid":2100184,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:46:05.000Z","msg":"參考韓國瑜粉絲團<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d0c4bb939ae99ef5c30432f6b494691688beb2","tid":2100184,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:47:12.000Z","msg":"即係叫d藍絲屌鳩中間聯盟唔夠紅唔好投佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}